The paper discusses the implications of using Blockchain technology for searchable encryption solutions, which involves topics related to cryptography (cs.CR), distributed computing (cs.DC), databases (cs.DB), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and software engineering (cs.SE). The focus on privacy and security vulnerabilities also suggests cs.CR as the most likely category.
